__ HEADLINE NEWS ________________________________________________________
 
Can You Hear Me Now: The True Role of Voice-directed Picking in Warehouse Management
-by René Jones

Although voice-directed picking may take distributors to higher logistics 
levels someday, operations managers should try listening to their warehouse 
personnel for now. Warehouse workers are the real experts on a company's 
warehouse, its product, and its customer.

